        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-09-15 19:07:48.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\ndocker-login is only needed when doing docker pull or push commands. \nThese jobs are just doing maven goals. \n\nI am happy to look into any failure on any of these jobs if you have one.",
        "patchset_number": 2
